source.note: This file is outside the repo; the hash pins the exact corpus used to generate counts.

notes.makamDetection: Heuristic: uses the first token of the 2nd T: line (if present) else 1st; keeps hyphenated forms; falls back to any word-like token if needed. Normalized keys strip diacritics and punctuation.
notes.kFormat: K: lines in this corpus often encode a 53-EDO microtonal key-signature-like accidental set (e.g. "K:C _1B^4f^4c") rather than major/minor.
